<HL> Currency Markets:
Dollar Shows
Small Losses
In Slow Market
---
Range Is One of Narrowest
Of Year as Traders See
Little Reason for Action
---
By Charles W. Stevens
Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal</HL>
<DD> 07/02/87</DD>
<SO> WALL STREET JOURNAL (J)</SO>
<IN> EUROP FREST JAPAN CANDA
